world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"cc8dc361ea7ebe3a9054e7d4c0803a2b700aaf44","tid":1631521,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:45:26.000Z","msg":"唔靠外國勢力<br />\n你點打贏<br />\n<br />\n唔好自我膨脹<br />\n爆下玻璃獅鳥幾個藍絲就好威呀"},{"pid":"10ce21c083af77c4e4a4586fb1c25cf23bd914df","tid":1631521,"uid":241762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:49:12.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"7139f6b23ef7ac93ec221489e301341acf754fee","tid":1631521,"uid":241762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc8dc361ea7ebe3a9054e7d4c0803a2b700aaf44","tid":1631521,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:45:26.000Z","msg":"唔靠外國勢力<br />\n你點打贏<br />\n<br />\n唔好自我膨脹<br />\n爆下玻璃獅鳥幾個藍絲就好威呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:51:16.000Z","msg":"幾時有話唔靠外國勢力? 我係話 &quot;部分&quot; 外國輿論唔使理會呀! 你閱讀理解未合格過?"},{"pid":"c7f405b2548867c69de3c62690fd56fda1b85fa1","tid":1631521,"uid":241762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:51:27.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"ceee4b98d59f7871a48b5725f5b9657578fc62b8","tid":1631521,"uid":241762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:51:37.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"a1e7e90f4ce0ed2837b1c8fc5e829758394817d5","tid":1631521,"uid":241762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201